a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>O construtor <strong><code>Option()</code></strong> cria novos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptionElement\"><code>HTMLOptionElement</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var optionElementReference = new Option(text, value, defaultSelected, selected);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"text\"><code>text</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> representa o conteúdo do elemento, o texto mostrado na tela. Se o texto não é especificado, o texto padrão \"\" (texto vazio) é utilizado.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"value\"><code>value</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> representa o valor do <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLOptionElement\"><code>HTMLOptionElement</code></a>, i.e. o valor do elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a>. Se não especificado, o texto é usado como valor, e.g. o elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a> tem seu valor associado quando o formulário é submetido ao servidor.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"defaultselected\"><code>defaultSelected</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Um <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> é usado para adicionar o atributo <strong>selected</strong>, para que este <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a> seja mostrado como selecionado no elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a> quando a página for carregada. Se não especificado, o estado padrão é não selecionado. Observe que o <strong>defaultSelected = true</strong> não define a opção como o valor selecionado do elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"selected\"><code>selected</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Um <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> é usado para colocar elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a> no estado de selecionado; como padrão do elemento tem o estado de não selecionado. Se omitido, mesmo que o parâmetro <strong>defaultSelected</strong> for verdadeiro, o elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a> não é selecionado.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"adicionando_novas_tags_options","title":"Adicionando novas tags options","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code> <span class=\"token comment\">/* assumindo que temos este HTML\n&lt;select id='s'&gt;\n\n&lt;/select&gt;\n*/</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> s <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'s'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Quatro<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Cinco<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Seis<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\noptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">elemento<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> chave</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    s<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>elemento<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> chave<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n <span class=\"token comment\">/* Resultado\n&lt;select id='s'&gt;\n    &lt;option value=\"0\"&gt;Quatro&lt;/option&gt;\n    &lt;option value=\"1\"&gt;Cinco&lt;/option&gt;\n    &lt;option value=\"2\"&gt;Seis&lt;/option&gt;\n&lt;/select&gt; */</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"adicionando_options_com_diferentes_parâmetros","title":"Adicionando options com diferentes parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* assumindo que temos este HTML\n&lt;select id=\"s\"&gt;\n    &lt;option&gt;Primeiro&lt;/option&gt;\n    &lt;option&gt;Segundo&lt;/option&gt;\n    &lt;option&gt;Terceiro&lt;/option&gt;\n&lt;/select&gt;\n*/</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> s <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'s'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> options <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token string\">'zero'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'um'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dois'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\noptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">elemento<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> chave</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>elemento <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'zero'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    s<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Option</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>elemento<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span cl